MP - mana points
HP - hit points

[Spell]  - a complete magic piece, made out of a [Phrase] and all the needed attributes we extract from it
[Phrase] - a skeleton of a spell from wich we will try to understand, what the spell does, how many MP costs and etc. Made out of [Words]
[Word]   - a piece of a pharse describing a particular attributue or behaviour trait.
